{"tid":1185928,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[摩笛追魂] 摩根士丹利指標警告衰退風險 2006年來第一次","createTime":"2019-06-04T14:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T18:09:07.000Z","uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c919cb6a924a4e62590e5d3ec4fd9dacbff03256","tid":1185928,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T14:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ei.marketwatch.com/Multimedia/2019/06/03/Photos/NS/MW-HK653_downtu_20190603083901_NS.png?uuid=90d6c2b8-85fc-11e9-9628-9c8e992d421e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fei.marketwatch.com%2FMultimedia%2F2019%2F06%2F03%2FPhotos%2FNS%2FMW-HK653_downtu_20190603083901_NS.png%3Fuuid%3D90d6c2b8-85fc-11e9-9628-9c8e992d421e&h=48dea2fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n摩根士丹利近日警告稱，其周期指標已經從「擴張」翻轉到了「衰退」，投資者應當為未來12個月里可能出現的市場震蕩做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n  摩根士丹利（Morgan Stanley）近日警告稱，投資者應當為未來12個月里可能出現的市場震蕩做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n  該行表示，其周期指標已經從「擴張」翻轉到了「衰退」，而從過去歷史來看，該信號出現后往往就是股市和其它資產走弱的開始，並且衰退的可能也在上升。<br />\n<br />\n  摩根士丹利認為，投資者們應當避險，用安全的債券或者現金來代替美股。<br />\n<br />\n  「美國經濟數據雖然高於均值，但在惡化中。我們的周期指標已經轉變，從2007年來第一次從『擴張』轉向了『衰退』。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n  該指標包括了經濟和金融市場數據，包括了債券收益率曲線的表現、消費者信心以及債務問題等。<br />\n<br />\n  當然，就報告來看，投資者還有足夠的時間能做好準備。<br />\n<br />\n  上一次該指標顯現出「衰退」信號的時候，還是2006年11月，當時美股還在高漲，金融危機爆發距離當時還有一段時間。<br />\n<br />\n  在這種情況下，摩根士丹利的分析師們認為，投資者不應冒險。在股市仍在高位，而貿易爭端繼續的情況下投資者們應當減持風險資產。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20190604/31518552.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20190604%2F31518552.html&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgtArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=a1a01aa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20190604/31518552.html</a>"},{"pid":"05151b86041138951026188fc618421865743018","tid":1185928,"uid":26553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"摩笛反操作9成贏錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60cd53506b5c72be62ba2c37199d364f9e5180f7","tid":1185928,"uid":66811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05151b86041138951026188fc618421865743018","tid":1185928,"uid":26553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:28:42.000Z","msg":"摩笛反操作9成贏錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38b62a69fa4c690c5cd8714974f401305d20aa3","tid":1185928,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"摩根士丹利預測特斯拉股價可能只值10美元 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661f9340a39cfa9483edc38f686c49e7cf74ae16","tid":1185928,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b38b62a69fa4c690c5cd8714974f401305d20aa3","tid":1185928,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:38:29.000Z","msg":"摩根士丹利預測特斯拉股價可能只值10美元 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:39:40.000Z","msg":"&quot;值&quot;"},{"pid":"2a85bebeb6ad3defbc43959afb5917bb06f34935","tid":1185928,"uid":140737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T15:45:02.000Z","msg":"佢呢排都搵夠錢啦，都想益下其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a466f17a5a7c44320821869f8d9f62870266b302","tid":1185928,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T18:06:53.000Z